description: This is the animation that plays when you win a game of Hearts in Windows Vista or 7. Seeing this animation is rare, because in Hearts, there are multiple rounds and the game only ends when a player reaches 100 points and obviously it also requires you to win the game.
fulltitle: Hearts win animation (Windows Vista/7 Card Game)

comments.text: I have never seen this animation before (despite of having played this game for many times 😂).
